beer.beer_description:
The perfect combination of hops and malt, there is a lot going on here. The caramel maltiness and tropical fruit/berries play against the lingering bitterness, making it a great beer to finish your session on. A cult favourite amongst our loyal fans. The complexity of this beer is like a rollercoaster of goodness. Strap yourself in!

Malt: Ale, Munich, Aurora, Shepard’s Delight

Hops: Simcoe, Mosaic, Citra

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

Get out there and raise a ruckus with your favorite Amber or Red Ale! That is 60 different beers with the style of American Amber / Red Ale, American Amber / Red Lager, Irish Red Ale, Imperial / Double Red Ale, Red Ale - Other or IPA - Red. Try 5 more for Level 13!

items.checkin_comment:
A good complex red, biscuity, berry and smooth.  Cracking colour as well.
Always good to get down to Tippler’s Tap at Southbank.
